                    'Our build review checklists reference a variety of training, best practices, and support resources so help is never far away. You can also access our legendary training academy.',
                    './assets/imgs/designer04.jpg','Learn Continuously',
                    'Productive developers are happy developers. Give your team all the support and tools they need to deliver consistent, quality solutions each and every time.',
