        +extent-block3('assets/imgs/manager03.jpg','RoboDesigner cuts delivery time by ~30% freeing your team to deliver more','“As a small shop, we couldn’t afford a Design Authority. RoboReview has given us this capability and enabled us to upskill our developers quickly. It has made a massive difference!”','RPA Program Lead, North American Bank','#EF4C3E')
